    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3031763172" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3031763172" />
    <a title="Jean" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/23100707-jean"><img alt="Jean" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1562348872p2/23100707.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3031763172?book_show_action=true">Nov 14, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jean" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jean" href="/user/show/23100707-jean">Jean</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=audio-book">audio-book</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=military">military</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=business">business</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=politics">politics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3031763172" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9998124448635568706">I was unaware of Rachel Maddow until I saw several interviews of her for her current book “Blowout”. I was impressed to learn that she is a Rhodes Scholar and has a Ph.D. in Politics. I watched a few of her shows and read this book. I am amazed at her analytical abilities. She can reduce complicated data into succinct, epigrammatic, perceptive and easy understandable information.<br/><br/>Maddow documents how the checks and balances of government have broken down. She says Congress has abdicated its respo</span>
  <span id="freeText9998124448635568706" style="display:none">I was unaware of Rachel Maddow until I saw several interviews of her for her current book “Blowout”. I was impressed to learn that she is a Rhodes Scholar and has a Ph.D. in Politics. I watched a few of her shows and read this book. I am amazed at her analytical abilities. She can reduce complicated data into succinct, epigrammatic, perceptive and easy understandable information.<br /><br />Maddow documents how the checks and balances of government have broken down. She says Congress has abdicated its responsibilities to debate, approve or disapprove of wars. The military relies too heavily on contractors and the executive branch find it too easy to go to war. Maddow’s use of antidotes and humor makes the book an easy read. I wish the book was a bit more neutral or evenly balanced, but I guess that would not be making her point as attention grabbing. I noted she said that the failure of the government’s checks and balances has placed the country in a dangerous place. This book was written in 2013.<br /><br />I read this as an audiobook downloaded from Audible. The book is seven hours and thirty-one minutes. Maddow narrated her own book.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="9998124448635568706" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

